英国奖2025：投票现已开放https://www.nme.com/news/music/music/brit-awards-2025-voting-now-open-3833576？Damian Jones Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:58:47 +0000 Music NewsNewsBRIT AwardsDanceHip-hopIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3833576 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>五个类别的获奖者将在今年由粉丝在英国人聊天中决定</p><p>英国<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-voting-now-open-3833576">邮政奖2025年：现在投票开放，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/charli-xcx@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>投票已经为谁在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年英国颁奖典礼</a>上获胜的人开放。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">这是2025年英国奖的所有提名人</a></strong></li></ul><p>The winners in five categories will be decided this year for the first time ever by fans in a BRITs WhatsApp chat, at the ceremony which will <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-revealed-for-the-brit-awards-2025-3794739">take place at The O2 in London on Saturday March 1</a> , and broadcast exclusively on ITV1 and ITVX.</p><p> Beginning today (January 31), fans can start a chat and follow the prompts to cast votes in the categories for Alternative/Rock Act, Dance Act, Hip Hop/Grime/Rap Act, Pop Act and R&amp;B Act <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone=447860003223&amp;text=Vote&amp;type=phone_number&amp;app_absent=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a> . Voting is open until 11:59pm on Friday, February 14 and votes can be cast in each category once per day.</p><p> A host of artists feature in Alternative/Rock Act including <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">The Cure</a> , who have received their first BRIT nominations in over three decades thanks to the critically-acclaimed album &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">Songs Of A Lost World</a> &#39;. </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/robert-smith-the-cure@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> The Cure&#39;s Robert Smith CREDIT: Barry Brecheisen/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p> They are up against <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beabadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Dinner Party</a> . In the Dance Act category, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> , who <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">leads the way with the most nominations</a> , receiving nods in five categories, goes up against <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">Becky Hill</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-status">Chase &amp; Status</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> .</p><p> Elsewhere in the Pop Act, Charli once again is competing against <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/myles-smith">Myles Smith</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-name-2025-rising-star-winner-3819335">the winner of the 2025 Rising Star Award</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jade-thirlwall">JADE</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lola-young">Lola Young</a> .</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave">DAVE</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ghetts">Ghetts</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> meanwhile lead the Hip Hop/Grime/Rap category while <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">RAYE</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cleo-sol">Cleo Sol</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/flo">FLO</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">Jorja Smith</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-kiwanuka">Michael Kiwanuka</a> will compete for the R&amp;B Act award. </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/DuaLipaGlastonbury-reflects.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa performs live at Glastonbury Festival 2024 CREDIT: Joe Maher/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> Sebastian Battista Simone, SVP Audience, Warner Records &amp; Parlophone and Co-chair of the BRITs Digital Committee said: “With billions of music fans across Meta&#39;s platforms, we&#39;re thrilled to expand the BRIT Awards partnership, by introducing WhatsApp as a new voting platform for the first time. Fans can now support their favourite artists directly within the app for public-voted categories, celebrating the artists with the most passionate and engaged communities.</p><p> “Combined with the power of Instagram Reels to amplify nominated artists, this collaboration ensures The BRITs reaches a global audience like never before.” </p><figure style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Myles-Smith-wins-the-2025-BRIT-Awards-Rising-Star.-CREDIT_-John-Marshall_JMEnternational.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> Myles Smith winner of the 2025 BRIT Awards Rising Star CREDIT: John Marshall/JMEnternational/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Earlier today, the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-first-performers-revealed-3833403">first performers at the ceremony were also announced</a> including JADE, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaboozey">Shaboozey</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">Teddy Swims</a> , The Last Dinner Party and Myles Smith.</p><p> More acts are expected to be announced in the lead-up to the awards ceremony in March.喜剧演员和演员 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-jack-whitehall-to-return-as-host-3829454">杰克·怀特霍尔（Jack Whitehall）被宣布为返回的主持人</a>，这是他在2018年，2019年，2020年和2021年举行的第五次举行仪式。</p><p> Back in November, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-brit-award-trophy-design-for-2025-revealed-3814651">the new trophy design was revealed ahead of the 2025 ceremony</a> .它是由著名的不列颠尼日利亚多学科艺术家加布里埃尔·摩西（Gabriel Moses）创建的，他多年来一直与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> ，Burberry等人合作。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-voting-now-open-3833576">BRIT Awards 2025: Voting now open</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
